<node TEXT="For most users this function is obsolete, having been replaced by the Pattern Manager available via the menu entry Format &gt; Physical Style &gt; Manage Patterns... However, for advanced technical users, the Text Patterns command loads custom-defined patterns from an optional file named patterns.xml located in the user&apos;s &quot;.freeplane&quot; home directory." ID="ID_368378276" CREATED="1271853008077" MODIFIED="1271853453381"/>
